{"tid":990964,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"好驚隻貓比人扔","createTime":"2019-01-22T04:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T03:48:09.000Z","uid":211656,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"03d08f639db92c558c83ed582ed4308562fb1508","tid":990964,"uid":211656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:33:16.000Z","msg":"養左隻貓6年 同成家人都相處得好好<br />\n<br />\n最近近老母疑似更年期加癡撚左線 乜都嘈一餐<br />\n<br />\n事源隻貓最日成日叫 每晚一定要同我瞓 （同老母一間房 我上架）<br />\n但佢前腳又跛跛地 要人抱上抱落既 所以佢就成日喵人要人抱佢上嚟<br />\n<br />\n有日老母話佢太嘈 要扔左佢去愛護 嚇撚到我喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩個一排佢冇咁做<br />\n<br />\n但嚟緊新年 成家都要出門三日 除老母<br />\n好驚個3日老母趁住成家人唔係屋企會扔左佢<br />\n我有咩方法可以保住隻貓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：好愛隻貓 唔會棄養<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd618b2c3933c4c9bfd4a3d117071b90715ce06","tid":990964,"uid":47479,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:35:13.000Z","msg":"掉左呀媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683417dbe0f87a1c9d2284a8778dde6eaafe98ef","tid":990964,"uid":211656,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0fd618b2c3933c4c9bfd4a3d117071b90715ce06","tid":990964,"uid":47479,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:35:13.000Z","msg":"掉左呀媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"有諗過趁佢唔係到換鎖"},{"pid":"6daf40418d2b9797b67c4814aa91e579e57a9700","tid":990964,"uid":210161,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:37:33.000Z","msg":"比朋友/寵物酒店照顧三日<br />\n起碼唔會因爲喵喵喵 挑起你老母把火"},{"pid":"d8ce3014c68e891039339b979421b035160e5e88","tid":990964,"uid":188310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"老母VS貓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n世界大戰抹黑宇宙了"},{"pid":"a9